      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just looking at some stuff about the heat death of the universe and it just hit me... like, why even bother? everything we do, every single feeling or achievement, it all just gets wiped out by entropy eventually. it feels like we're just playing a game that’s already been lost. it's kind of hard to find a reason to keep pushing through the day when the end result is just... nothingness.",
